OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,FThe boss of a mental health charity
OL,7,Fhas blamed ideological failings and
OL,8,Funder resourcing for the series of
OL,9,Fevents which led to Valdo Calocane
OL,10,Fgoing on to kill three people and
OL,11,Finjure three others in Nottingham in
OL,12,F2023.
OL,14,FA Care Quality Commission (CQC) report
OL,15,Fhas found numerous failings in the way
OL,16,Fmental health services dealt with
OL,17,FCalocane, who killed 19-year-old
OL,18,Fstudents Barnaby Webber and Grace
OL,19,FO'Malley-Kumar before killing 65-year-
OL,20,Fold Ian Coates in the early hours of
OL,21,F13 June.
