OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,F'The same litany of faults is repeated
OL,7,Fagain and again'
OL,9,FMarjorie Wallace is the founder and
OL,10,FCEO of SANE, a mental health charity.
OL,12,FShe has been involved in more than a
OL,13,Fhundred inquiries and reports into
OL,14,Fhomicide cases like this and 'can see
OL,15,Fonly too well how errors like this
OL,16,Fhappen.'
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/15
