OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,F"The attitude and culture need to
OL,7,Fchange, we need to treat patients
OL,8,Findividually, there cannot be a quota
OL,9,Ffor the number of people detained or
OL,10,Fnot detained.
OL,12,F"We need to make it possible for
OL,13,Fpeople to access care and treatment
OL,14,Fwhen they need it, not when the crisis
OL,15,Fpoint has come. We need to listen to
OL,16,Fpatients, families and carers.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/15
