OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,F"But it doesn't mean that it isn't
OL,7,Fterrible for the families where there
OL,8,Fare the victims and it doesn't mean
OL,9,Fthat there aren't a lot of near misses
OL,10,Fwhere people could easily put
OL,11,Fthemselves and others at risk, because
