OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Healthcare Chief
OL,7,FExecutive, Ifti Majid said:
OL,9,F"We acknowledge and accept the
OL,10,Fconclusions of this report and have
OL,11,Fsignificantly improved processes and
OL,12,Fstandards since the review was carried
OL,13,Fout. Our teams have much more contact
OL,14,Fwith people waiting to be seen in the
OL,15,Fcommunity to agree crisis plans and
OL,16,Fensure they have an up-to-date risk
OL,17,Fassessment even when they are
OL,18,Fstruggling to engage with our services
OL,19,For primary care.
