OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,F"Colleagues are also working to
OL,7,Fimprove alignment between our teams,
OL,8,Fprimary care and talking therapies,
OL,9,Fhelping to reduce waiting times as
OL,10,Fwell as communicate more effectively
OL,11,Fwhen patients move between services or
OL,12,Fdisengage from treatment.
OL,14,F"We have a clear plan to address the
OL,15,Fissues highlighted and are doing
