OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,FWes Streeting MP, the Health
OL,7,FSecretary, says the number of failures
OL,8,Fhighlighted in the CQC report is
OL,9,Fshocking.
OL,11,FVictoria Atkins MP, Shadow Health and
OL,12,FSocial Care Secretary, said:
OL,14,F"At this difficult time, my thoughts
OL,15,Fand deepest sympathies are with the
OL,16,Ffamilies of Barnaby, Grace, and Ian.
OL,17,FThey have suffered horrific losses
OL,18,Fwhich they feel every minute of every
OL,19,Fday. When I met them, I promised them
OL,20,Fthat we would seek answers for them
OL,21,Fthrough this report.
