OL,3,CWhy did the mental health care for
OL,4,Ckiller Valdo Calocane go so wrong?
OL,6,F"I want to thank the CQC for their
OL,7,Fdiligent work in conducting this
OL,8,Freview into this horrific incident.
OL,10,F"It is important that we reflect on
OL,11,Fthe findings and recommendations,
OL,12,Fincluding accepting and addressing
OL,13,Fwhere failures have been identified,
OL,14,Fin order to ensure that other families
OL,15,Fdo not have to experience this same
OL,16,Fsuffering.
